<h2>New Service Assigned to You</h2>
<p>Hello <strong>{{accountantName}}</strong>,</p>
<p>A new service request has been assigned to you. Please review the details and begin processing at your earliest convenience.</p>

<div class="details-box">
  <div class="details-row">
    <span class="label">Client Name</span>
    <span class="value">{{clientName}}</span>
  </div>
  <div class="details-row">
    <span class="label">Service</span>
    <span class="value">{{serviceName}}</span>
  </div>
  <div class="details-row">
    <span class="label">Reference ID</span>
    <span class="value">{{referenceId}}</span>
  </div>
  <div class="details-row">
    <span class="label">Status</span>
    <span class="value">In Progress</span>
  </div>
</div>

<a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="btn">View Service Request</a>
<p>Please log in to the portal to access all related documents and form data.</p>
